column5: A friend of mine from work told me he had herd someone fell in at the dam ... fire rescue and opp at the dam and copter flying over river on sunday ... anybody hear anything?

Yes was at steves bait and tackle yesterday  In dunville Some of you may know it as fishmasters i had been fishing all day and stopped into say hi. Apparently a 82 yr old gentleman fell in and drowned.  Very SAD!! Especially being so close to christmas.
searched some info ... police still havent found the missing man  http://www.dunnvillechronicle.com/webapp/s...ssif=News+Alert
